---
title: "Volunteering in Fingertips: Tsinghua University Education Foundation's Support for Summer Social Practice Teams"
collection:
type: "Video Production"
permalink: /medias/2023-10-27-fingertip-public-welfare
venue: "Tsinghua University Education Foundation"
date: 2023-10-27
location: "Beijing, China"
---
This initiative report and accompanying video, produced and conceptualized by [Your Name], highlight the "Fingertip Public Welfare" project by the Tsinghua University Education Foundation. This project is a micro-donation platform that leverages alumni contributions to support social practice teams. The video showcases the impactful work of student teams across China, such as music education programs in Xinjiang and art and science outreach in rural communities. Through creative storytelling and visual representation, [Your Name] illustrates the strength of alumni-student bonds, highlighting the meaningful contributions these teams make in underserved areas.

